# Bookshelf Layout & Aesthetic Verification Checklist

- [ ] Navigate to http://localhost:3000 and ensure the latest version is loaded (hard refresh if needed).
- [ ] Verify webpage background features:
  - [ ] Gorgeous vertical paneling wallpaper.
  - [ ] Oak parquet floor lines are rendered.
  - [ ] Warm spotlight glow makes the cabinet stand out.
- [ ] Verify bookcase dimensions and look:
  - [ ] Beautifully compact and tall.
  - [ ] Max width limit: `max-w-[620px]` and height limit: `h-[670px]` (no scrollbars).
- [ ] Verify all books and ornaments are absolutely perfect (Lisa Simpson, Lucky Cat, green leaning book, Bunny Plush, Potted Plants, etc.).
- [ ] Capture verification screenshot and save as artifact.
